                499

                501

                514

                515

                516

                518

                519
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                520

                521
            

            

                
            

            

                
    if (state->x.have == (state->size << 1)) {

            

        

            

                522

                523

                524
            

            

                
            

            

                
    }

            

        

            

                525
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                526

                529

                530

    state->x.have++;

    state->x.next--;

    state->x.next[0] = (unsigned char)c;

            

        

            

                537

                538

                540
